title: Total Cross-Section for Gamma - Production By Inelastic Interaction of Fast Neutrons With Light, Intermidiate and Heavy Nuclei

x4codes.shortRef: Conf: 3.All Union Conf.on Neutron Phys.,Kiev,9-13 Jun 1975, Vol.4, p.133 (1975)

x4freetext: BY INELASTIC INTERACTION OF FAST NEUTRONS
WITH LIGHT, INTERMIDIATE AND HEAVY NUCLEI
ZR-T TARGET IN A HOLLOW SPHERICAL SAMPLE
THOUSE WERE MADE ON GAMMA SELF-ABSORPTION
7. PC, NEUTRON FLUX ERROR 3. PC,  GAMMA
CHANGED, AUTHOR NAMES GORBACHJOV TO GORBACHEV
